Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to lead to a 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' after 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in successful payment requests
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER and the end of the case

Name: Time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases where this path is followed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in cases that were initially rejected by any role before approval
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' in the process variants leading to a payment without prior rejections
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time it takes for a case to be 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' after any rejection
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in successful cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
